&lt;h2 id=&quot;december&quot;&gt;December:&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;December was another guest heavy month. In fact I only had two days where I didn&amp;#39;t have someone staying at my place. Annie visited for a week, which was a lot of fun. Then my Mom crashed on my couch for a week. Then my Dad and brother came (just Travis stayed with me), and the whole family was in town for a week for Christmas. Then Mom and Dad went home and Travis and I celebrated his Birthday and the New Year together. It was a blast.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flickr.com/photos/icco/15369937674&quot; title=&quot;2014-12-10 16.10.19 by Nat Welch, on Flickr&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7583/15369937674_dfb646ec7d.jpg&quot; width=&quot;205&quot; &gt;&lt;/a&gt;
