&lt;h2 id=&quot;next-year-i-plan-to&quot;&gt;Next year I plan to...&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Figure out a way to build and ship products as part of my job. I really miss creating things for a living, and I am pretty sure it&amp;#39;s the basis for a lot of my stress, so I am going to focus on getting that right. I still haven&amp;#39;t turned that into OKRs, but I&amp;#39;m working on it, and will have a post out about that as well soon-ish.&lt;/p&gt;

