So why can&amp;#39;t I spend Sunday in the city? Because I&amp;#39;m running in Wharf to Wharf.  Yes, I&amp;#39;m stupid, I know, leave me alone. So pray for me, and lend me your athletic ability while you sleep till a reasonable hour.&lt;/p&gt;

